6
00:00:47,675 --> 00:01:01,675
Stage 3: geospatial orchestration. Engines, rescue, ambulance routed from the nearest station, ETA computed live.

7
00:01:00,697 --> 00:01:14,697
And the dispatcher CAD entry — incident summary, unit assignment, scene safety brief — drafted by the Kamiwaza-deployed model.

8
00:01:13,714 --> 00:01:23,714
DISPATCH — runs inside your accredited environment. Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
